  m_sTitle "Capturing Objectives"
  m_sTextData "Redfor must be in 90% control of their objectives for their respective capture times."\
  "It takes 2 minutes for each gun position, and 5 minutes for the town. "\
  ""\
  "Recapturing Objectives is not possible for Blufor, but they can reset the capture timer by entering the objective radius."\
  ""\
  "Radius are not marked to prevent meta-gaming but they fully encompass each feature."\
  ""\
  "There will be no messages to indicate capturing progress, the only message will appear when the Redfor has captured one."
